headline: Asana to Announce Third Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results on Tuesday, December 2, 2025
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, November 03, 2025--Asana, Inc. (NYSE: ASAN)(LTSE: ASAN), a leading work management platform for human + AI collaboration, announced today that it will release financial results for the third quarter fiscal year 2026 on Tuesday, December 2, after the close of the U.S. markets.

headline: Accenture (ACN) Fell in Q3 Amid Strong Growth Trajectories
summary: Columbia Threadneedle Investments, an investment management company, released its “Columbia Global Technology Growth Fund” third-quarter 2025 investor letter.
